name: Space Doge Army from the Mission to Mars OG collection by PulseUNITY

metadata.name: Space Doge #1
metadata.description: Doges are in Space and it is the year Pulse UNITY 2069! Spacecamp has been set up on MARS where 10'000 SPACE DOGE ARMY are waiting to train for their 1st Mission.Bank of Mars has set up staking so that the Doge Army can earn PLSU whilst in training. To help the war Bank of Mars will be doing further PLSU CHART BUY BACKS to maintain buy pressure and rewarding Ethereum to all recruits that complete basic training!Follow the Mission to Mars at spacecampmars.com whilst watching a live feed from NASA.
